data.description: On the River in New Bern, NC - Your Next Home or Investment!Discover a lovely spot on the river in New Bern, NC! This property comes with 2 cute cottages, each with its own beautiful view of the water. Live in one, and consider the many possibilities for the second!Main Cottage: Enjoy cozy living in the heart of nature. With space to relax and a sunroom for gazing at the river, it's a perfect little getaway.Second Cottage:Two bedrooms and just as much charm! A handy place for guests or other opportunities.Plus, a 2-car garage gives you plenty of space for parking and storage.Not only do you get a beautiful home, but you also minutes away from downtown New Bern. With the river right there, fun times fishing or just enjoying the view are right on your doorstep.
